              "free_text": [
                "- By Author -",
                "1.  In the first series of spectra, when yield of",
                "Pr-138m was measured, no Ce-139 could be found which",
                "indicates that the 140-Ce(p,n+p)139-Ce reaction must",
                "have a very low cross section at proton energy below",
                "32 MeV. For the process no cross section data have been",
                "published yet.",
                "2. Ce-139 gamma spectra was recorded after three days",
                "to measure quantitatively the long-lived radioisotopes."
              ]
